{"tid":584490,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"想當年 smartone話無限上網會搞到佢地蝕本","createTime":"2018-03-08T00:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T08:20:17.000Z","uid":32577,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3d89dbecb8ef32ff3c5e8881317df1a96c37588f","tid":584490,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:17:16.000Z","msg":"精彩內容重溫:<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20120203/16038624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120203%2F16038624&d=9xCj0ZM2kNV1B6IO2JeSoy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=bdffb5f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120203%2F16038624&h=7f1f9496\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20120203/16038624</a><br />\n<br />\n黎大鈞又說，把無限上網調整為每月2GB，是根據現客戶使用量而定，該台現時約85%客戶的平均每月用量為1.5GB，「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">畀2GB佢哋其實仲有剩</span></span>」。但他承認，智能手機用戶在兩年內急升7倍，令電訊商的成本壓力急增，也是促使取消無限上網的原因之一，更承認取消無限上網「封咗蝕本門」。此消息令其股價昨升13%<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f039accdfb6ded2c44c830d1b20992856de2ca67","tid":584490,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:20:04.000Z","msg":"仲有話過自己大把錢<br />\n未驚過添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4a99436b9398f50abb4ace7251e73562ef1c1a","tid":584490,"uid":32577,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:23:11.000Z","msg":"而家啲plan越嚟越平，為左滿足客户犧牲自己，良心企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f637e24aa7838ffbc94c527d8987ecaeec554a74","tid":584490,"uid":16756,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f039accdfb6ded2c44c830d1b20992856de2ca67","tid":584490,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T00:20:04.000Z","msg":"仲有話過自己大把錢<b